headline: Bio-Techne Announces Release of GMP TcBuster Non-Viral Genome Engineering System
summary: Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ: TECH), a leading provider of innovative life science research tools, is pleased to announce the official release of GMP Transposase mRNA for the TcBuster™ non-viral genome engineering system, supporting the development and manufacture of immune cell- and stem cell-based therapies.
